data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
The Night's Watch is a military order which holds and guards the Wall, the immense fortification which guards the northern border of the Seven Kingdoms. As a member of the Night's Watch you should defend The Wall from the White Walkers, who are trying to conquer the north.
Your task is to kill the upcoming waves of White Walkers. There is a new wave every 15 seconds. If there are more then 15 White Walkers alive on the screen, you lose the game.
Kill this kind of White Walker (see picture) by klicking him with the cursor. Each kill will give you 1 score point.
Kill this kind of White Walker (see picture) by doubleklicking him with the cursor. Each kill will give you 5 score points.
Try not to kill Night's Watch members (see picture). Each kill will lower your life points by 1 and your score points by 5 . If yo lose all of your life points you lose the game.
This CannonBalls (see picture) are aiming the Night's Watch members. If they touch them,they will die and you lose life points. Try to destroy them before they reach your allied Night's Watch member.
There are 3 levels,each level is 60 seconds long. Survive the 3 levels to win the game. Good Luck.
